title: spanish Omelette
description: A hearty omelette packed with potatoes, onions, and sometimes bell peppers, giving it a delightful blend of flavors and textures, perfect for a savory start to your day.

title: Plain Omelette
description: A classic omelette, fluffy and light, made simply with eggs, seasoned to taste, ideal for those who enjoy a straightforward, delicious egg dish.

title: Scrambled Eggs
description: Soft and creamy scrambled eggs, lightly seasoned and cooked to perfection, a versatile breakfast staple enjoyed by all.

title: French Toast
description: Thick slices of bread soaked in a mixture of eggs and milk, fried to a golden brown and dusted with powdered sugar or cinnamon, a sweet breakfast delight.

title: Pancake
description: Light, fluffy pancakes served hot, often enjoyed with syrup, butter, or fresh fruit, making for a delightful and filling breakfast.

title: Pancake Egg Roll
description: A creative twist combining the lightness of a pancake rolled with an egg filling, offering a mix of flavors and textures in every bite.

title: Chicken Lollipop (Wings)
description: Juicy chicken wings marinated in spices, battered, and deep-fried until crispy, served with a tangy dipping sauce for an extra kick.

title: Chips Masala
description: French fries tossed in a spicy, tangy tomato-based sauce, offering a flavorful and zesty twist on classic fries.

title: Chips Poussin
description: Crispy French fries served with a topping of poussin sauce, blending spices and savory flavors for a unique fry experience.

title: Chips Plain
description: Classic French fries, golden and crispy, lightly salted and perfect on their own or as a side to any meal.

title: Beef Samosas (3pcs)
description: Crispy triangular pastries filled with spiced minced beef, deep-fried to a golden brown, offering a savory and crunchy snack.

title: Vegetable Samosas (3pcs)
description: Golden and crispy pastry pockets filled with a mix of seasoned vegetables, a perfect vegetarian snack.

title: Hot Spicy Beef Samosas
description: A spicier take on the classic beef samosa, with a filling that’s packed with extra heat and flavor for those who like it hot.

title: Egg Sandwich
description: A satisfying sandwich filled with a creamy egg mixture, seasoned to perfection, ideal for a quick, delicious meal on the go.

title: Hot Dogs
description: Juicy sausage nestled in a soft bun, served with classic toppings like mustard, ketchup, or relish, a beloved fast-food favorite.

title: Sausages (2pcs)
description: Savory sausages, grilled or fried, with a juicy interior and crisp exterior, perfect for breakfast or a snack.

title: Beef Kebabs
description: Skewers of seasoned ground beef, grilled to bring out the rich flavors, a delicious option for a snack or appetizer.

title: Baked Beans
description: Tender beans cooked in a rich, slightly sweet tomato sauce, a comforting and hearty side dish that pairs well with breakfast or any meal.

title: Full Breakfast
description: A hearty meal featuring a combination of eggs, toast, sausages, bacon, and often beans or grilled tomatoes, perfect for a satisfying and balanced start to the day.

title: Continental Breakfast
description: A lighter breakfast option, typically including pastries, fresh bread, butter, jam, and coffee or tea, ideal for those looking for a quick, delicious morning bite.

title: Hot Chocolate
description: A comforting, rich drink made with warm milk and cocoa powder, smooth and sweet, perfect for warming up on a chilly day.

title: Pre-Mixed Pot of Tea
description: A classic pot of tea brewed and mixed to the right strength, ready to be enjoyed plain or with milk and sugar, perfect for tea lovers.

title: English Grey Tea
description: A fragrant black tea with a hint of bergamot, offering a unique citrus aroma, a refined choice for a sophisticated tea experience.

title: Masala Tea
description: A spiced tea blend with warming flavors of ginger, cardamom, and cloves, offering a fragrant and invigorating drink with a touch of sweetness.

title: Strong Coffee
description: Bold and robust coffee brewed to a stronger intensity, perfect for those who need an extra kick of caffeine to start their day.

title: Mild Tea
description: A lightly brewed tea, gentle in flavor, ideal for a relaxed drink that’s not too strong yet still comforting.

title: Cocoa with Milk
description: A creamy, chocolatey drink made with cocoa powder and milk, providing a smooth, sweet treat enjoyed by all ages.

title: Glass of Milk
description: Fresh, cold milk served in a glass, nutritious and refreshing, perfect on its own or alongside breakfast.

title: Assorted Fruit Juice
description: A selection of fresh fruit juices, offering a refreshing and vibrant blend of flavors, packed with vitamins to kickstart your morning.

title: Mineral Water
description: Pure, refreshing mineral water, served chilled or at room temperature, perfect for hydration at any time of day.

title: Soda
description: A refreshing carbonated drink available in a variety of flavors, a popular choice for a bubbly, sweet treat.

title: Avocado Puree & Vanilla Ice Cream
description: A creamy and unique dessert featuring smooth avocado puree paired with vanilla ice cream, offering a delightful contrast of flavors and textures for a refreshing treat.

title: Full Chicken (Local)
description: A whole locally sourced chicken, cooked to perfection, offering tender meat with rich, natural flavors, perfect for sharing or as a centerpiece for any meal.

title: Chicken Stew (1/4)
description: A flavorful quarter chicken cooked in a savory broth with vegetables and spices, creating a comforting, tender dish with rich flavors in every bite.

title: Chicken Wet Fry (1/4)
description: A quarter chicken cooked in a thick, spicy sauce, tender and juicy, ideal for those who love a saucier, robust flavor.

title: Chicken Dry Fry (1/4)
description: A quarter chicken dry-fried with aromatic spices and herbs, resulting in a crispy, flavorful dish without sauce, showcasing the rich flavors of the chicken.

title: Fish Dry Fry
description: Fresh fish dry-fried with spices until crispy on the outside and tender inside, a deliciously simple and flavorful way to enjoy fish.

title: Fish Wet Fry
description: Fresh fish cooked in a thick, spiced sauce, making it juicy and tender with a deep, savory flavor, perfect for pairing with sides like ugali or rice.

title: Boiled Fish
description: Fresh fish boiled in a light broth, delicately seasoned to bring out its natural flavors, ideal for a simple, nutritious meal.

title: Local Vegetable
description: A medley of locally sourced leafy greens, lightly sautéed or steamed, seasoned simply to retain their natural taste and nutrients.

title: Beef Wet Fry
description: Succulent pieces of beef cooked in a thick, spiced sauce, tender and flavorful, great for pairing with traditional sides.

title: Beef Dry Fry
description: Spiced beef fried until crispy and flavorful, without sauce, creating a savory dish with a delicious, bold taste.

title: Beef Boiled
description: Tender beef pieces boiled in a seasoned broth, capturing the essence of the meat’s natural flavor in a light, comforting dish.

title: Ugali
description: A staple food made from maize flour, cooked into a dense, smooth texture, perfect for pairing with any stew, vegetable, or fried dish.

title: Rice
description: Fluffy, steamed rice, a versatile side that complements a variety of dishes with its light and neutral flavor.

title: Chapati
description: Soft, layered flatbread, pan-cooked until golden, with a slightly crispy edge, perfect for scooping up stew or enjoying as a side.
